Maybe you should have mentioned that your application does not even run, it exits with an error. In general, it is pretty much a mess. Maybe you should have tested it and looked into the logs before publishing it on GitHub. You also should have posted log output showing the errors instead of just basically saying &quot;it does not work&quot;. I had to fix many things:

