* In your task aspects `Task{1,2,3}` the pointcut `execution(public com.spring.aspect.interfaces.entity.Job com.spring.aspect.interfaces.process.GenericProcessImpl.process(..)) &amp;&amp; args(context)` is invalid because neither is there a `GenericProcessImpl.process(..)` method nor does it have a `Context` argument. what you have instead is a `void execute()` method with no arguments.

