if you&#39;re trying to pass the &#39;check&#39; variable to this view function from another route, a common way of doing so is using the route decorator. I.e.:


    @app.route(&#39;/sortbysalary/&lt;check&gt;&#39;, methods=[&#39;POST&#39;])
